The Electron Neutrino · node ATM · ATM · A nearly massless, chargeless lepton that interacts only via the weak force — so weakly that trillions pass through you each second unnoticed.

universe of origin : ATM · The Atom
seal               : BALANCES BETA DECAY. Emitted (as its antiparticle) whenever a neutron decays, carrying off energy and conserving the books. The ghost particle that lets the weak force do its bookkeeping.
